title: Members1st FCU Mobile
description: Members 1st Federal Credit Union Mobile Banking allows you to view balances, transfer funds, view history and pay bills on the go! For qualified accounts, you can even make a deposit from your phone!Use our branch and ATM locator to find a branch or ATM close to your current location!*Mobile Banking is for registered Online Banking users only.
descriptionHTML:
Members 1st Federal Credit Union Mobile Banking allows you to view balances, transfer funds, view history and pay bills on the go! For qualified accounts, you can even make a deposit from your phone!

Use our branch and ATM locator to find a branch or ATM close to your current location!

*Mobile Banking is for registered Online Banking users only.
comments: cumbersome and buggy.  easily the worst banking app I have used.  very unhappy my car note is serviced by this company due to this app
Can't view my transaction history anymore for some reason. I need to know how much is getting deposited jnto my account!
Old version worked this one stinks. Won't let me access my account.  Not worth using at all.
This update is much smoother. Probably the smoothest version yet.
Misplace your thumb on your fingerprint scanner once, and it locks your account.

recentChanges: Just in time for the holiday season:
- We were busy in our workshop improving branch locator and mobile deposit, especially on that newer device you bought as a gift to yourself.
- For the reindeer, we have improved support for those Oreo devices they love so much.
- We gave some coal to those bugs on our naughty list, particularly those that may have caused the app to stop working for some of you.
Happy Holidays!  We hope you enjoy our free gift to you.
